---
title: Middle Eastern Harissa-Glazed Chicken with Roast Pumpkin, Garlic Yoghurt & Pear Salad
description: Sit back and bathe in the glow of this vibrant dish. The harissa glaze makes the succulent chicken shine and elevates the protein to sweetened heights whilst also bringing out those beautiful spiced flavours. A roast pumpkin on the side warms up the plate to later be cooled down by a pear salad.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
